se-al-yusr","tag-hardship","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-sadness-al-huzn","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-aII","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17372,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/four-things-happiness-misery\/","url_meta":{"origin":41212,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Living: Four things part of happiness, misery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFour things are part of happiness: a righteous spouse, a spacious dwelling, a righteous neighbor, and a comfortable mount. Four things are part of misery: a bad neighbor, a bad spouse, a restrictive dwelling,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/27\/dua-anxiety-depression\/","url_meta":{"origin":41212,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication against anxiety and depression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNever is a servant struck by worry or grief but let him say, \u2018O Allah, I am Your servant, the son of Your servant, the son of Your maidservant. My forelock is in Your hand,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonl